room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz: Maximum Security" by Escape Room Zone in Detroit
review: Very fun! Will be going back. We did Prison Break. It was difficult, but not scary or high pressure!

room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz: Maximum Security" by Escape Room Zone in Detroit
review: My friends and I escaped from Prison Break last night! Jovan made sure my birthday celebration was exciting and fun. I will definitely be going back to try a different room soon!

room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz: Maximum Security" by Escape Room Zone in Detroit
review: We just finished the Prison Break room and even though we didn't escape in time, we had a blast! It was definitely very challenging and kept us entertained for the whole time. Big kudos to Jovan for being an awesome guide! He was friendly, upbeat, and definitely gave us some much-needed clues!
